      "text": [
        "1323 - وَ رَوَى عَنْهُ مَنْصُورُ بْنُ حَازِمٍ أَنَّهُ قَالَ: «اَلْقِيرُ مِنْ نَبَاتِ اَلْأَرْضِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1323 - Mansur ibn Hazim reported from him (Abu Abdullah (as)) that He said: \"Pitch (tar) is from the vegetation of the earth.\""
        ]
      }
